Code 1:
```
print("Type the time for the 10km run, type 0 to end")
number = 0
time = 0
time_input = float(input("Enter time you ran for 10km"))
while time_input!=0:
 number += 1
 time = time_input + time
 time_input=float(input("Enter time you ran for 10km"))
else:
 print("Your average time is " , time / number)
```
